---
import Layout from "../layouts/index.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-p:indent-4 prose-p:text-base md:prose-p:text-lg lg:prose-p:text-xl xl:prose-p:text-2xl text-justify font-extralight text-balance hyphens-manual md:my-12"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3 tracking-[0.2em]"
    >
      <h1
        class="text-left text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
      >
        Meet me, Yusoof Moh
      </h1>
      <div
        class="not-prose flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase shadow-inner ring-1 ring-slate-200 transition dark:bg-slate-900/70 dark:text-slate-300 dark:ring-slate-700"
      >
        <span class="font-semibold tracking-[0.3em]">Bio mode</span>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="relative inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-[0.7rem] font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-800 uppercase shadow transition hover:bg-slate-50 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-slate-400 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-700"
          data-mode-toggle
          data-state="detail"
          aria-pressed="false"
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true" data-label-detail>Switch to TL;DR</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="hidden" data-label-tldr
            >Switch to full bio</span
          >
          <span class="sr-only"
            >Toggle between full biography and TL;DR views</span
          >
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div data-mode="detail" class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        In the name of Allah, and by His grace. My name is pronounced <i
          >yu-soof</i
        >. Born and raised in Malang, now collaborating remotely across
        Indonesia. I am a
        <strong>full-stack engineer</strong> building reliable products for SMEs.
        <strong>Web:</strong> TypeScript/React (TanStack), Node/Bun, Hono;
        <strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker, Traefik, CI/CD;
        <strong>Mobile:</strong> React Native/Capacitor;
        <strong>Observability:</strong> Sentry, SigNoz. Recently, I have been standardizing
        CI/CD across monorepos and shipping a
        <strong>multi-tenant booking &amp; operations platform</strong> (web + mobile)
        end-to-end&mdash;from schema and APIs to Docker Swarm deployments and dashboards.
        Beyond code, I cultivate edamame, enjoy regional motorcycle tours, and keep
        a steady habit of deep research. I base my understanding of Islam in accordance
        with the first three generations of the ummah, focusing on <strong
          >tawhid</strong
        >
        and <strong>tafsir</strong>. To further that commitment, I conduct
        private
        <i>tahsin</i> classes and support local Muslim communities, aspiring to contribute&mdash;however
        small&mdash;to the da'wah.
        <span class="font-semibold"
          >Open to meaningful remote/contract collaborations.</span
        >
        You can reach out via
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id"
          onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Mail</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/twitter"
          onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/linkedin"
          onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/github"
          onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">GitHub</a
        >. May Allah bless our endeavors, and lead us to His everlasting mercy.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div data-mode="tldr" class="hidden space-y-4">
      <p>
        Bismillah. I'm a Malang-based, remote
        <strong>full-stack engineer</strong> for SMEs delivering end-to-end
        <strong>TypeScript/React (TanStack)</strong>, Node/Bun, Hono systems
        with Docker, Traefik, CI/CD, React Native/Capacitor mobile, and
        observability via Sentry/SigNoz, currently shipping a
        <strong>multi-tenant booking &amp; operations platform</strong> while pursuing
        deep research, edamame cultivation, regional motorcycle tours, and Islamic
        learning centered on <strong>tawhid</strong> and <strong>tafsir</strong>
        through private <i>tahsin</i> classes, open to meaningful
        <strong>remote/contract collaborations</strong> via
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id"
          onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Mail</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/twitter"
          onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/linkedin"
          onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/github"
          onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">GitHub</a
        >. Baarakallahu fiik.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script is:inline>
    const toggle = document.querySelector("[data-mode-toggle]");
    const detail = document.querySelector("[data-mode='detail']");
    const tldr = document.querySelector("[data-mode='tldr']");

    if (toggle && detail && tldr) {
      const detailLabel = toggle.querySelector("[data-label-detail]");
      const tldrLabel = toggle.querySelector("[data-label-tldr]");

      toggle.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const showingDetail = toggle.dataset.state !== "tldr";
        toggle.dataset.state = showingDetail ? "tldr" : "detail";
        toggle.setAttribute("aria-pressed", showingDetail ? "true" : "false");

        detail.classList.toggle("hidden", showingDetail);
        tldr.classList.toggle("hidden", !showingDetail);

        detailLabel?.classList.toggle("hidden", !showingDetail);
        tldrLabel?.classList.toggle("hidden", showingDetail);
      });
    }
  </script>
</Layout>
